I&#x27;ve used this one for so many things and it&#x27;s awesome.<p>I&#x27;ve downloaded a whole youtube channel, downloaded videos as mp3&#x27;s and what not.<p>I have couple of aliases set in my .zshrc too :)<p>mp3dl() {
youtube-dl --extract-audio --audio-format mp3 $1
}<p>root@haseebr7 ~ mp3dl <youtube_video_url><p>and bam i have the mp3 download. I no longer have to visit shitty ad infested websites to do these kind of things.
